data.description: Motivated Sellers!!!  This is the one you've been looking for if you are needing lots of space at an affordable price?  Location, location, location! This home is in the heart of Sherwood where there are great schools and shopping  in the central Arkansas area.  This home has a huge living room with plenty of room for a dining area.  Nice size Kitchen with a large breakfast bar. Closet off of kitchen can be used as a pantry closet.  There is a nice size bonus room that can be used as a game room, office, craft room or a guest bedroom (no closet accessible to this room). This home is being sold as is. Square feet is approximate.  Agents see "AGENT REMARKS".
